{"sections":{"main":{"type":"main-page","disabled":true,"settings":{"padding_top":28,"padding_bottom":28}},"rich_text_yEwYBe":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_LNzDY7":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"<strong>OUR CORK FOOTWEAR<\/strong>","heading_size":"h2"}},"text_Kf3zwM":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Our cork sandals and mules are meticulously handcrafted in the beautiful Murcia region of Spain, with materials handpicked from selected local suppliers.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["heading_LNzDY7","text_Kf3zwM"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"center","content_alignment":"center","color_scheme":"","full_width":true,"padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":12}},"image_banner_8k9enj":{"type":"image-banner","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/cork-factory-spain.webp","image_overlay_opacity":0,"image_height":"adapt","desktop_content_position":"middle-center","show_text_box":true,"desktop_content_alignment":"center","color_scheme":"","image_behavior":"none","mobile_content_alignment":"center","stack_images_on_mobile":true,"show_text_below":true}},"rich_text_mwNXpV":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_MhTzeE":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"<strong>SANDGRENS FOOTBEDS<\/strong>","heading_size":"h2"}},"text_6HhyER":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>We offer two options for you to choose from, the original footbed and the cushioned footbed. <\/p>"}}},"block_order":["heading_MhTzeE","text_6HhyER"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"center","content_alignment":"center","color_scheme":"","full_width":true,"padding_top":28,"padding_bottom":12}},"multicolumn_N8zpnc":{"type":"multicolumn","blocks":{"column_63UFpj":{"type":"column","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/102-01-B-SAGEGREEN-BR-2.webp","title":"<strong>Original footbed<\/strong>","text":"<p>Our original footbed features a pure cork mold with a traditional cork mix, offering classic comfort and support. The footbed is crafted with a thin suede inlay directly on top of the cork sole.<\/p>","link_label":"","link":""}},"column_DeRcqd":{"type":"column","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/1004-01-B-SANDSTONE-BR-3.webp","title":"<strong>Cushioned footbed<\/strong>","text":"<p>The cushioned footbed takes the comfort of cork to the next level. It shares the same cork mold and mix as the original footbed but incorporates a 5.3mm latex foam layer between the cork sole and the suede inlay.<\/p>","link_label":"","link":""}},"column_mDV3Un":{"type":"column","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/footbed.webp","title":"<strong>Key differences<\/strong>","text":"<p>The original footbed stands out for its ability to mold and shape your foot over time, providing a personalized and comfortable fit. In contrast, the cushioned footbed offers enhanced cushioning with a latex foam layer for those who desire extra support and comfort.<\/p>","link_label":"","link":""}}},"block_order":["column_63UFpj","column_DeRcqd","column_mDV3Un"],"settings":{"title":"","heading_size":"h1","image_width":"full","image_ratio":"adapt","columns_desktop":3,"column_alignment":"left","background_style":"none","button_label":"","button_link":"","color_scheme":"","columns_mobile":"1","swipe_on_mobile":true,"padding_top":8,"padding_bottom":0}},"rich_text_yPmNtq":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_QzJ3b6":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"<strong>CAREFULLY SOURCED, HANDPICKED LEATHER<\/strong>","heading_size":"h2"}},"text_QJQYwk":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>All our leathers for our cork footwear are sourced locally in Murcia, Spain. They are REACH compliant and come from tanneries that are members of the Leather Working Group (LWG), ensuring environmentally responsible practices.<\/p>"}},"button_49iLYm":{"type":"button","settings":{"button_label":"Understanding REACH","button_link":"https:\/\/echa.europa.eu\/regulations\/reach\/understanding-reach","button_style_secondary":false,"button_label_2":"","button_link_2":"","button_style_secondary_2":false}}},"block_order":["heading_QzJ3b6","text_QJQYwk","button_49iLYm"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"center","content_alignment":"center","color_scheme":"","full_width":true,"padding_top":44,"padding_bottom":20}},"multicolumn_qpbL6B":{"type":"multicolumn","blocks":{"column_4MLKpG":{"type":"column","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/vienna_00b3ec1f-aafd-46b6-bfd0-4b059f01e01f_kopiera.webp","title":"<strong>Oiled nubuck<\/strong>","text":"<p>This full-grain oiled nubuck leather is known for its exceptional quality and durability. With a thickness of 2.4 - 2.6 mm, this leather offers a robust and slightly oiled texture, providing a unique pull-up effect that enhances its aesthetic appeal.<\/p>","link_label":"","link":""}},"column_wUPrYF":{"type":"column","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/soria-magenta.webp","title":"<strong>Dry nubuck<\/strong>","text":"<p>This premium nubuck leather, is renowned for its soft yet durable texture. With a thickness of 2.0 - 2.2 mm, this delicately sanded, full-grain leather offers a refined and elegant finish.<\/p>","link_label":"","link":""}},"column_iapmi9":{"type":"column","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/102-01-V-BLACK-BL-1.webp","title":"<strong>Corrected leather<\/strong>","text":"<p>Our premium top grain genuine leather features a buffed and shiny finish that exudes sophistication and refinement. With a substantial thickness of 2.4 - 2.6 mm, this leather boasts a robust and enduring quality. <\/p>","link_label":"","link":""}}},"block_order":["column_4MLKpG","column_wUPrYF","column_iapmi9"],"settings":{"title":"","heading_size":"h1","image_width":"full","image_ratio":"adapt","columns_desktop":3,"column_alignment":"left","background_style":"none","button_label":"","button_link":"","color_scheme":"","columns_mobile":"1","swipe_on_mobile":true,"padding_top":8,"padding_bottom":0}},"rich_text_RpnHra":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_BkjNkf":{"type":"heading","settings":{"headi